import React from "react";
import {
  View,
  StyleSheet,
  SafeAreaView,
  ScrollView,
  Dimensions,
  Image,
  Text,
  TouchableOpacity,
  TextInput,
} from "react-native";
import Colors from "../Constants/Colors";
import PersoButton from "../Components/persoButton";
import { ceil } from "react-native-reanimated";

let screenWidth = Dimensions.get("window").width;
const Profile = (props) => {
  return (
    <SafeAreaView>
      <ScrollView>
        <View style={styles.header}>
          <Image
            style={{ width: screenWidth * 0.5, height: 90, marginTop: 30 }}
            source={require("../assets/logoNav.png")}
          />
        </View>

        <View style={styles.container}>
          <View
            style={{
              overflow: "hidden",
              marginVertical: 30,
              borderRadius: screenWidth * 0.1,
              borderWidth: 2,
              borderColor: Colors.dark_grey,
            }}
          >
            <Image
              style={{
                width: screenWidth * 0.36,
                height: screenWidth * 0.36,
              }}
              source={require("../assets/sun.jpg")}
            />
          </View>
          <Text style={styles.title}>Informations de la terre:</Text>

          <View style={styles.firsCard}>
            <View
              style={{
                width: "48%",
              }}
            >
              <View style={styles.left}>
                <Text style={styles.title}>Superficie</Text>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>1200 hectares</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.left}>
                <Text style={styles.title}>Latitude</Text>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>195.554</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.left}>
                <Text style={styles.title}>Longitude</Text>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>32.001</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View
              style={{
                width: "48%",
                justifyContent: "space-evenly",
              }}
            >
              <View style={styles.right}>
                <Text style={styles.title}>Ville</Text>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>Mostaganem</Text>
              </View>
              <View style={styles.right}>
                <Text style={styles.title}>Type de terre</Text>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>manich 3aref</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
          </View>
          <PersoButton style={{ ...styles.button, marginBottom: 20 }}>
            Modifier les info de la terre
          </PersoButton>
          <View style={styles.card}>
            <View style={styles.titleContainer}>
              <Text style={styles.title}>Informations personneles:</Text>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Nom</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>El mogherbi</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Prenom</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>Mohammed Fayçal</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Numero télephone</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>0552776099</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>E-mail</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>m.elmogherbi@esisba.dz</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Mot de pass</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>**********</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Numéro ccp</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>0123456789</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Numéro carte banquaire</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>0123456789</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <View style={styles.itemHolder}>
              <Text style={styles.text}>Numéro carte edahhabia</Text>
              <View style={styles.textHolder}>
                <Text style={styles.inputTexte}>0123456789</Text>
              </View>
            </View>
            <TouchableOpacity activeOpacity={0.6}>
              <Text
                style={{ color: Colors.primary, fontSize: screenWidth * 0.065 }}
              >
                Modifier
              </Text>
            </TouchableOpacity>
          </View>
        </View>
      </ScrollView>
    </SafeAreaView>
  );
};

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  header: {
    height: 90,
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
  },
  container: {
    elevation: 30,
    backgroundColor: "white",
    borderTopLeftRadius: 40,
    borderTopRightRadius: 40,
    justifyContent: "flex-start",
    alignItems: "center",
    overflow: "hidden",
    paddingBottom: 20,
  },
  firsCard: {
    flexDirection: "row",
    width: screenWidth * 0.92,
    justifyContent: "space-between",
    marginTop: 20,
  },
  right: {
    backgroundColor: Colors.whiteSmoke,
    borderRadius: 20,
    width: "100%",
    height: screenWidth * 0.375,
    elevation: 4,
    justifyContent: "space-evenly",
    alignItems: "center",
    marginBottom: 10,
    paddingVertical: 20,
  },
  left: {
    backgroundColor: Colors.whiteSmoke,
    borderRadius: 20,
    width: "100%",
    height: screenWidth * 0.25,
    elevation: 4,
    justifyContent: "space-evenly",
    alignItems: "center",
    marginBottom: 10,
  },
  card: {
    borderRadius: 30,
    backgroundColor: Colors.whiteSmoke,
    width: screenWidth * 0.92,
    marginBottom: 25,
    elevation: 4,
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center",
    paddingBottom: 15,
  },
  titleContainer: {
    borderTopLeftRadius: 30,
    borderTopRightRadius: 30,
    padding: 8,
    backgroundColor: Colors.whiteSmoke,
    width: "100%",
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
    marginBottom: 10,
  },
  title: {
    fontFamily: "open-sans-bold",
    fontSize: screenWidth * 0.05,
    color: Colors.dark_grey,

  },
  itemHolder: {
    alignItems: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
    width: "90%",
    marginBottom: 20,
  },
  textHolder: {
    width: "100%",
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderColor: Colors.grey_fade,
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center",
    padding: 10,
    borderRadius: 10,
    backgroundColor: "white",
    marginTop: 5,
  },
  text: {
    fontSize: screenWidth * 0.05,
    fontFamily: "open-sans",
    color: Colors.dark_grey,
    alignSelf:"flex-start"
  },
  inputTexte: {
    color: Colors.dark_grey,
    fontSize: screenWidth * 0.045,
    fontFamily: "futura-meduim",
  },
  button: {
    backgroundColor: Colors.primary,
    paddingHorizontal: 20,
    borderRadius: 10,
  },
});

export default Profile;
